'''Umjing Baab and His Swinging Trio''' were an orchestra-[[Band/Legends|band]] that performed on the ''[[Queen of Empire]]''. Songs of theirs included "[[Smoky Dreams]]" and "[[Mood and Moons]]." They played several genres of [[Music/Legends|music]], including [[swing-bop]] and modern [[Jizz/Legends|jizz]] selections.

Though the band's name might seem to imply a total of four members including bandleader [[Umjing Baab]], Baab was apparently considered a part of the "swinging trio", as there were only two other members in the group. All three band members were of the [[Rughja]] species.

[[Bria Tharen]], while traveling undercover as a cabaret singer named "[[Bria Tharen|Bria Lavval]]," once performed with the group.

